  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600315809830-B60BZRB6T3956EI24ITF/22a-scaled_e1356549574-429x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Really enjoyed working with these kits this month. Ended up making 10 layouts using the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/block-party-scrapbook-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">Main kit</a>, as well as add-on's <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/wildberry-court?aff=6cc2c70f\">Wildberry Court</a>, <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/pioneer-drive?aff=6cc2c70f\">Pioneer Drive,</a> and <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/woodbrooke-road?aff=6cc2c70f\">Woodbrooke Road</a>. Here is my main kit only layout:</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600315830128-MU65SWA3L503WO4V15JH/22b-littleandiSC-558x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Love the piece of printed vellum as well as the blue twine that came in the kit. The chipboard Thickers are perfect for painting with acrylics. Once I finished the Main Kit Only layout, I started playing around with the Add-On's.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"22c-current-randomSC-566x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600315864774-P5AJ34LKBEE3LCY65I98/22c-current-randomSC-566x600.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"22d-these2SC-560x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600315864930-8UDDJUC0IYLKE9H15EG2/22d-these2SC-560x600.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"22e-youmeSC-560x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600315865809-QRFVV2ABXIH53DAPZVO4/22e-youmeSC-560x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22f-good-morningSC-560x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600315865724-P7BP3A47HSWVM83F6TZL/22f-good-morningSC-560x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22g-stkildaSC-559x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600315866372-AHKCLSUU5ATIALZN8XNR/22g-stkildaSC-559x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>One of the best Christmas presents I received is from my dear friend <a href=\"http://www.danacolwell.com/index2.php#/home/\">Dana Colwell</a>. While Mommy and I were in Maui, she arranged to get the dogs to her house to take some photos of them. I am blown away with her talent and her wicked gift-giving skills. Couldn't resist using this one:</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600315896908-JAJWRVPSIY7S2W3UNKX4/22h-allearsSC-445x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>For all the layouts, visit the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/creative-team-gallery/block-party/scrapbook/amy-tan--2?aff=6cc2c70f\">gallery</a>. supplies: <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/block-party?aff=6cc2c70f\">Studio Calico January kits - Block Party</a> Add Ons: <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/wildberry-court?aff=6cc2c70f\">Wildberry Court</a> || <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/pioneer-drive?aff=6cc2c70f\">Pioneer Drive</a> || <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/woodbrooke-road?aff=6cc2c70f\">Woodbrooke Road</a></p>"
